return {title = "Red Key", id = "580", description = {'While held, a red outline of a door will appear on certain walls. Using the Red Key near it will spawn a red room', "Attempting to create a room outside the maximum boundary (13 x 13 rooms) of the map will take you to an I AM ERROR room. You can't use the Red Key to leave this room", "The Red Key can be used to open the secret room in the Home floor, which is the method for unlocking alternative 'Tainted' characters", 'In rooms with multiple door outlines, the closest one will be opened', 'This room will randomly choose from many types, including (but not limited to) any regular room from that floor, treasure rooms, curse rooms, devil rooms, angel rooms, I AM ERROR rooms and more'}}